@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uzorvn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.04 * v0 + 0.01)) + wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.59)))
    v1 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.62)) / 0.15)
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v2 + 0.83) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.83)))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.58 - v0 + 0.21) * (v0 + 0.49 + v1 + 0.82)))
    tmp = 0.26
    data[tid] = v0
